desc_short	-----								XBridge is a 2D shooter online game set in the SciFi ReVeN universe. Construct your own levels and share them with the world using our intuitive built-in level editor. Compete in local and online coop modes as well as a single player story driven campaign. Explore a procedurally generated space environment packed with enemies and bosses.							
developer									Varia Games								
